extendedInfo.description: This is the free version of Soap Bubbles Live Wallpaper.Check out the paid version for more features, like:- Set a background image- Special Soap Bubbles (Heart, Star, Cube)- Unlimited bubble colorsAvailable languages: English, GermanFeatures and settings:- Set how many bubbles should fly- Different sizes- Set a list of colors used to colorize the bubbles(only up to 3 colors in the free version, unlimited in the paid version)- Set the background color of your screen- Mix the color of the bubbles with the background(This feature can cause a decrease of performance)
